name: White_or_Black_Plastic_Folding_Chair
description:
Plastic folding chairs are the choice of many event planners for their lightweight design, ease of cleaning, and versatility among events. This folding chair will make a practical choice in the home or for hosting outdoor events. The textured seat ensures safe and comfortable seating. After an event you can stack them on top of each other or in a row. To make transporting even easier, equip yourself with the appropriate sized folding chair dolly to make event management more effortless.
